<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>300</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zài yī gè liáng fēng qī qī de yè wǎn dà wèi kàn shǒu yáng qún zài bó lì héng de shān jiān
 tā zhī dào huì yǒu shī zi de chū xiàn bù tíng dǎo gào zàn měi yǔ shén qīn mì jiāo tán
 xīn lǐ zhēn píng ān shén shì hù wèi gān shén de líng gǎn dòng tā xiě xià zhe míng shī piān
 wǒ men de hǎo mù zhě lǐng wǒ men zài xī shuǐ biān wǒ men yǒng yuǎn gēn zhe tā xiàng hǎi ōu bù lí hǎi miàn</lyrics>
<title>shén shì hù wèi gān 迦南300</title>
</song>